descriptionHtml:
This game is about aiming at the target and shooting different objects like round targets, barrels, animal targets like dinosaurs, reptiles, hens, cows, buffalos, and fruits like apple shooting, watermelon shooting, bottle shooting, etc.
There are many different vector dinosaurs to shoot some of them are :
Tyrannosaurus rex (T-rex), Argentinosaurus, Avimimus, Aragosaurus, Archaeopteryx, Ankylosaurus, Amargasaurus, Archaeoceratops etc.

Controls :
➼ Simple Touch Controls.
➼ Tap and hold the screen to aim, release to shoot.
➼ Make sure to aim for the highest point and shoot.
➼ There is no time limit, you can shoot when even you are at the top score or point.

Make the highest score and compete with friends by sharing your score and game with them.

descriptionHtml:
Unleash your inner marksman with Slingshot Master: 3D Shooter! This engaging game challenges you to aim precisely and hit a variety of dynamic targets, offering hours of fun and skill development.
Game Features:

✔ Diverse Targets: Challenge yourself by shooting at a wide range of targets, including standard round targets, barrels, animal figures such as dinosaurs and reptiles, farm animals, fruits like apples and watermelons, bottles, and more.

✔ Simple Touch Controls: Enjoy intuitive controls—tap, hold, aim, and release to shoot.

✔ No Time Limits: Take your time to aim for the highest scores without any pressure.

✔ Competitive Play: Share your high scores and challenge friends to beat your record.
How to Play:

Tap and hold the screen to aim.
Adjust your angle and power to target the highest point.
Release to shoot and watch your projectile hit the target.

Why Play Slingshot Master: 3D Shooter?

If you're looking for a game that combines skill, precision, and fun, Slingshot Master: 3D Shooter is perfect for you. With its variety of targets and straightforward gameplay, it offers endless entertainment.
Download Now and Become the Ultimate Slingshot Master!

Test your shooting skills and aim for the top in Slingshot Master: 3D Shooter. Download today and embark on a thrilling shooting adventure!
